node.text:
One of the best Sneaker artists in the game, Mache joined us last week to show how to customize the Reebok Question Low 'White Ice.' The goat @theofficialai3 made a surprise appearance during the session, and discussed his impact on fashion & sneaker culture, and his Hall of Fame career! 

Watch for a few tips on how to customize a sneaker, and make sure to pick up the Question Low online and in-store.
